steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"8jc0g","text":"In each nucleofection, use 1 µg total of plasmid","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"f3rg7","text":"For prime editing PE2 strategy, use:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":18,"length":12}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fl2h6","text":"    500 ng pCMV-PE2","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"elunk","text":"    500 ng pU6-pegRNA","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"advmf","text":"For prime editing PE3 strategy, use:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":18,"length":12}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"951b8","text":"    500 ng pCMV-PE2","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"edou1","text":"    330 ng pU6-pegRNA","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"71isj","text":"    170 ng pBPK1520-ngRNA","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"ec3cn","text":"Pipet the proper amount of each plasmid into a microcentrifuge tube. If the volume is too small, dilute in autoclaved water first. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
